page1 = "CHANGE. PROGRESS. UNDERSTANDING. THIS IS [color=#1773E3]MAGIC[/color]. IT IS A PROCESS. IT IS AN ACTION ONE PERFORMS. [color=#1773E3]MAGIC[/color] IS THE CHISEL WITH WHICH WE CARVE INTO THE [color=#1773E3]ALETHIC[/color] FORCE. WITH IT, WE MAY DARE TO HOPE THAT ALL WILL NOT RETURN TO [color=#700f46]CHAOS[/color]."
